              {
                "type": "output_text",
                "text": "To solve the equation \\(\\sin(x) + x^2 = 42\\), we need to find the value(s) of \\(x\\) for which this equation holds true.\n\nLet's solve it numerically as it can't be solved algebraically. We'll look for real solutions.",
