            "container_id": "cntr_69d55e7129248190b100a58cbe9d596c073607be6dd7edfb",
            "code": "import numpy as np\nfrom scipy.optimize import fsolve\n\n# Define the equation\ndef equation(x):\n    return np.sin(x) + x**2 - 42\n\n# Guess values (since x^2 is 42, x is about sqrt(42) ≈ 6.48)\ninitial_guess_positive = np.sqrt(42)\ninitial_guess_negative = -np.sqrt(42)\n\n# Find the roots\nsolution_positive = fsolve(equation, initial_guess_positive)[0]\nsolution_negative = fsolve(equation, initial_guess_negative)[0]\n\nsolution_positive, solution_negative",
